{"tid":1162152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"面對依啲仆街可以點處理","createTime":"2019-05-19T16:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T16:27:21.000Z","uid":155667,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c1d95579fe42b17465933dec4537a6b6ccdf6ef","tid":1162152,"uid":155667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:23:40.000Z","msg":"事源FB睇到有人$250賣個wifi蛋同耳機就問佢有無<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Dx7nK6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Dx7nK6.png&h=6850f3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efKUNcB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefKUNcB.png&h=4876757b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好啦話有話寄 一直都唔覆唔寄<br />\n到覆啦就話唔見左差電座 由佢啦未話要耳機<br />\n搞一輪又無啦啦話寄左 黎到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZPhfwEW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZPhfwEW.png&h=9dd9fe4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n變左垃圾5蚊耳機 封哂塵 貨不對版<br />\n質問佢佢話我地搵錯買家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢又入到又聯絡到黎到又係佢個Wifi蛋<br />\n好意思屈返我地搵錯人<br />\n轉頭個改埋個post話唔係賣果個耳機<br />\n算數叫佢退錢寄返啲野比佢仲話要唔知咩事要搞清楚<br />\n到肯退錢話要我地比30蚊佢搭車去拎 傻撚左<br />\n過左幾日佢都未覆要退錢<br />\n好老實250小數目 係為啖氣 好地地做咩要比你呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有佢電話 地址 可以點做？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CzNORJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCzNORJO.png&h=0f52f224&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電話：62235449<br />\n大家隨便玩"},{"pid":"ad74800d50739eb0d10ab8758074f68f54105126","tid":1162152,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:26:14.000Z","msg":"幫佢叫外賣啦"},{"pid":"1c8491a83ec8a8000f63205bd994f553e2ed56f6","tid":1162152,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T16:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}